Cross-Framework Design System built with Ionic + Stencil, designed for accessibility, theme flexibility, and reusable Web Components compatible with Angular, React, Vue, and Vanilla JavaScript.


# ğŸŒ Corporate Design System

A modern, reusable, and accessible **Design System** built with [StencilJS](https://stenciljs.com/) and [Ionic Framework](https://ionicframework.com/) to deliver **Web Components** ready for use across **Angular**, **React**, **Vue**, and **Vanilla JavaScript** applications.

---

## ğŸ“Œ Project Goals

- âœ… Provide a consistent and scalable UI across corporate front-end apps
- âœ… Guarantee **accessibility** (WCAG 2.1 compliant wherever possible)
- âœ… Support **dark and light themes** using CSS custom properties
- âœ… Deliver reusable components via **Web Components**
- âœ… Make it framework-agnostic and easy to adopt

