## ğŸ§± Technologies Used

| Layer        | Technology                  |
|--------------|-----------------------------|
| Components   | [Ionic](https://ionicframework.com/) + [Stencil](https://stenciljs.com/) |
| Styling      | [Sass (SCSS)](https://sass-lang.com/) with CSS variables |
